---
title: So Delizioso Chicken Cutlets with Cheesy Mashed Potatoes and Tomato Zucchini Jumble
description: These chicken cutlets are coated in our So Delizioso Italian seasoning, which has a mix of flavorful herbs like oregano, basil, and parsley. So that must translate to so delicious, right? Bingo! Although the meat definitely isn’t the only delicious part of this dish—the cheesy mashed potatoes and sautéed zucchini and tomatoes are *molto bene*, too.
